name: Lunar Lander (itch) (cchickenwingss)
description:
Lunar Lander, try reaching the surface of the moon without getting crushed by asteroids. Use your thruster to avoid asteroids and your laser to destroy them, the laser can also extract fuel from kling-asteroids. Fullscreen is recommendend

Left/Right: A/D

Thruster: Space

Laser On/Off: E

Made for mini jam 130: lunar in 2 days.
